#: src-en/data/events_special_aea_old.xml:340
msgid ""
"data/events_special_aea_old.xml$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_DESTROYED_AEA_OLD\"]/text[2]"
msgstr "你不禁想，从前怎从未听闻过利尔米克族，旋即又记起自己是被他们绑架过来的。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_aea_old.xml:341
msgid ""
"data/events_special_aea_old.xml$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_DESTROYED_AEA_OLD\"]/text[3]"
msgstr "每摧毁一艘利尔米克星舰，你便离逃离他们的隔离区更近一步。虽仅是一小步，却也足"
"以支撑你继续前行。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_aea_old.xml:349
msgid ""
"data/events_special_aea_old.xml$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_DEAD_CREW_AEA_OLD\"]/text[1]"
msgstr "当最后一名利尔米克族倒下时，它吐出最后两个字：“去……你的……”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_aea_old.xml:350
msgid ""
"data/events_special_aea_old.xml$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_DEAD_CREW_AEA_OLD\"]/text[2]"
msgstr "你干净利落地解决了这些外星人。你毫无愧疚，毕竟这根本算不上谋杀。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_aea_old.xml:351
msgid ""
"data/events_special_aea_old.xml$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_DEAD_CREW_AEA_OLD\"]/text[3]"
msgstr "你听说过，利尔米克族并不会真正死亡，只是被重新导向新的躯体。但愿那些新躯体不"
"会出现在附近。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_aea_old.xml:352
msgid ""
"data/events_special_aea_old.xml$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_DEAD_CREW_AEA_OLD\"]/text[4]"
msgstr "或许你对利尔米克族毫无愧疚，但他们的有机船员未必都罪有应得。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_aea_old.xml:357
msgid ""
"data/events_special_aea_old.xml$//eventList[@name=\"AEA_OLD_SURRENDER_LIST\"]/event/text"
msgstr "\"很好，我看你比大多数人都要聪明。感谢我们也决定对你施以仁慈。\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_aea_old.xml:360
msgid ""
"data/events_special_aea_old.xml$//eventList[@name=\"AEA_OLD_SURRENDER_LIST\"]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "放过对方。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_aea_old.xml:364
msgid ""
"data/events_special_aea_old.xml$//eventList[@name=\"AEA_OLD_SURRENDER_LIST\"]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "干掉这些混蛋。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_aea_old.xml:366
msgid ""
"data/events_special_aea_old.xml$//eventList[@name=\"AEA_OLD_SURRENDER_LIST\"]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "\"真的吗？你还敢再和我们斗？哈，好笑。\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_aea_old.xml:376
msgid ""
"data/events_special_aea_old.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_AEA_OLD_ALL_SURRENDER\"]/surrender/text"
msgstr "\"凡人，你一定不知道你的行为的后果。我们并不是要去死。杀了我们，你们将遭受可怕的命运。\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_aea_old.xml:378
msgid ""
"data/events_special_aea_old.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_AEA_OLD_ALL_SURRENDER\"]/surrender/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "放过对方。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_aea_old.xml:382
msgid ""
"data/events_special_aea_old.xml$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_AEA_OLD_ALL_SURRENDER\"]/surrender/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "我们并不害怕你。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_aea_old.xml:426
msgid ""
"data/events_special_aea_old.xml$//ship[@name=\"AEA_OLD_STATION_EXCLUSIVE\"]/surrender/text"
msgstr "“行行，让你们进站，别杀我们就行。”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_aea_old.xml:428
msgid ""
"data/events_special_aea_old.xml$//ship[@name=\"AEA_OLD_STATION_EXCLUSIVE\"]/surrender/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "放他们一条生路。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_aea_old.xml:431
msgid ""
"data/events_special_aea_old.xml$//ship[@name=\"AEA_OLD_STATION_EXCLUSIVE\"]/surrender/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "你获准进入空间站，发现它基本上就是个巨大的商店。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_aea_old.xml:436
msgid ""
"data/events_special_aea_old.xml$//ship[@name=\"AEA_OLD_STATION_EXCLUSIVE\"]/surrender/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "解决他们。"
